name: CookieRun: The Darkest Night ~ Chapter1 ~
summary:
⚔️New Roguelike Challenge Arrived!⚔️

Dive into the Chaos Realm! 'Battle & Rush' before the Chaos Portal closes! Every playthrough promises a challenge and fun as you race down a changing 30-floor tower.
🍪 New Skills: Enhance your strategic play by summoning 6 companion cookies and using their power! 
🍪 New Weapons: The Magic Crossbow takes the gameplay to another level. The explosive area damage of the Boomstick! 
🍪 Leaderboard: Check your rankings on the leaderboard and see how you stack up against...
